comments: Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Smith's (BKN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Smith (BKN) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) contests the shot and initiates contact with Thomas' (BKN) lower body, affecting the jump shot attempt.
Thomas (BKN) and Booker (PHX) both pursue the loose ball, as Thomas gains possession Booker initiates contact and grabs his arm.
While defending the dive marginal contact occurs as Thomas (BKN) momentarily places two hands and then immediately removes them from Bridges' (PHX) body.  Bridges SQBR is not affected.
Bridges (PHX) is moving alongside Thomas's (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
O'neale (BKN) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).

Booker (PHX) is retreating, and he absorbs the contact initiated by Thomas (BKN) during the driving shot attempt. As Thomas enters his upward shooting motion Booker swipes up and cleanly dislodges the ball without making contact to Thomas' arm.
Warren (BKN) commits a take foul on Craig (PHX).
Claxton (BKN) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Bridges (PHX) initiates contact with Thomas' (BKN) arm during the drive and affects Thomas's (BKN) SQBR.
Smith (BKN) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
Bridges (PHX) commits a take foul on Thomas (BKN).
Thomas (BKN) commits a take foul on Ayton (PHX).
